sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>Gray CSS - Base</name><style>/**********************************************************
			Default Site - Font Selectors & Rules    Default gray is #767676
			***********************************************************/
			HTML {
			height: auto;
			}
			
			.section_header_content_no_scroll { /* applies to scrollable content area of form (area below the form title) */
			overflow: visible;
			height: auto; /* in IE6-8, if this is set to 100% then the scroll appears then disappears making the form jump in width, the auto attribute fixes this. */
			}
			
			html.section_header_html_no_scroll body.msie9 {
			overflow-y: auto; /*  It would act only when page opens in new window for IE9 */
			}
			
			
			BODY {
			height: auto;
			margin: 0px;
			padding: 0px;
			border: 0;
			font-weight: normal;
			font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif;
			}
			
			DIV.cms_layout_container{
			width:100%; 
			padding:0px; 
			margin:0px; 
			position:relative;
			}
			
			TABLE.cms_layout_table {
			margin: 0px;
			padding: 0px;
			border-collapse: collapse;
			width:100%;
			}
			
			p div.test {
			
			}
			
			/****** List and Column header background color styling ********/
			
			TR.header, TR.List_header, DIV.caption, .list_table thead th.list_hdrcell, .context_item.context_menu_hover, TH.list_hdrcell, TH.list_hdrcell A.column_head{
			background-color: #ffffff;
			color: white;
			}
			
			tr.list_header th{
			background-color: #ffffff;
			}
			
			/****** Header Styles **********************
			********************************************
			TD.cms_layout_content_header{
			
			}**/
			
			DIV.content_header_container{
			padding:0px; 
			margin:0px;
			}
			
			
			TABLE.content_header_table{
			border-collapse:collapse; 
			padding:0px; 
			margin:0px;
			}
			
			TD#dropzone0{
			border-bottom: 12px solid white;
			}
			
			
			/****** Content Body Styles ****************
			********************************************/
			
			TD.cms_layout_content_body{
			}
			
			DIV.content_body_container{
			padding:0px; 
			margin-bottom:100px; 
			}
			
			TABLE.content_body_table{
			border-collapse: collapse; 
			padding:0px; 
			margin:0px; 
			}
			
			TD#dropzone20{
			vertical-align: top;
			text-align: left;
			padding:0px; 
			margin: 0px 12px; 
			border-left: 12px solid white;
			border-right: 12px solid white;
			}
			
			TD#dropzone10{
			vertical-align: top;
			text-align: left;
			}
			
			
			/****** Footer Styles **********************
			********************************************
			TD.cms_layout_content_footer{
			
			}**/
			
			DIV.content_footer_container{
			padding:0px; 
			margin:0px; 
			}
			
			TABLE.content_footer_table{
			border-collapse: collapse; 
			padding:0px; 
			margin:0px;
			}
			
			TD#dropzone100{
			vertical-align: bottom;
			text-align: center;
			font-size: smaller;
			color: #FFFFFF;
			}
			
			
			
			/******* Buttons *******/
			
			BUTTON, INPUT.button, BUTTON.header {
			padding: 2px 6px 2px 6px;
			background-color: #868686;
			color: #FFF; 
			border: 1px solid #646464;
			}
			
			BUTTON:hover, INPUT.button:hover, BUTTON.header:hover {
			background-color: #6699cc;
			color: #FFF; 
			border: 1px solid #969696;
			}
			
			BUTTON.disabled {
			color: #999;
			background-color: #e0e0e0;
			border: 1px solid #AAA;
			}
			
			BUTTON.login {
			background-image: #868686;
			color: #FFF; 
			border: 1px solid #327bdd; 
			}
			
			BUTTON.stealth {
			border-width: 0px;
			background-color: white;
			}
			
			BUTTON.header, BUTTON.header:hover {
			font-weight: normal;
			margin-right: 5px;
			}
			
			BUTTON.widebutton {
			WIDTH: 100%;
			font-weight: normal;
			margin-right: 5px;
			background-color: #868686;
			color: #FFF; 
			border: 1px solid #646464; 
			}
			
			BUTTON.nav_header_button {
			font-weight: normal;
			margin-right: 5px;
			background-color: #868686 url(gray_cms_button_background.pngx) repeat-x center center;
			color: #FFF; 
			border: 1px solid #646464;
			}
			
			/* Service Catalog styles */
			a.cms_link_catalog_item:hover {
			text-decoration: none;
			}
			
			/* Knowledge Base styles */
			.kb_header_row, .kb_header_title_row, div.kb_add_info {
			display: none;
			}
			
			div.kb_article_header_short_description {
			display: block !important;
			font-size: 15pt;
			font-weight: bold;
			padding-bottom: 4px;
			color: #404040;
			}
			
			div.cms_knowledge_link_subtext, div.cms_catalog_link_subtext,  div.cms_request_link_subtext {
			color: #999999;
			font-size: .86em;
			}
			
			
			/* Search styles */
			.searchgroupheader {
			width: 100%;
			}
			
			.searchgroupheader img {
			/*display: none;*/
			}
			
			.searchgroupheader td {
			padding-left: 0px;
			}
			
			#searchBoxAndPrefs table {
			width: 100%;
			}
			
			div.text_search_kb, div.text_search_catalog {
			margin-left: 4px;
			}
			
			span.search_no_results {
			display: none;
			}
			
			span.searchfilterdisplay {
			display: none;
			}
			
			span.catalog_summary_bookmark {
			display: none;
			}
			
			/******* CMS Admin Pages *******/
			div.search_background {
			border: 1px solid #EBEFF9;
			padding: 0px;
			margin: 0px;
			background: url(gray_portal_horizontal_bkg.pngx) repeat-x center bottom; 
			height: 100px;
			margin-bottom:12px;
			}
			
			div.search_block {
			border: 0px;
			margin: 0px 0px 10px 10px;
			padding: 12px;
			white-space: nowrap;
			}
			
			span.search_examples {
			font-size: smaller;
			color:#666;
			}
			
			p.search_links {
			font-size: smaller;
			margin: 0px;
			padding: 0px; 
			}
			
			span.search_title {
			font-size: larger;
			}
			
			
			DIV.admin_nav_menus {
			width: 214px;
			}
			
			DIV.cms_admin_comments {
			background-color:#f6f6f6;
			color:#999;
			border: 1px solid #eee;
			padding: 18px;
			margin: 12px 0px 12px 0px;
			-moz-border-radius: 4px;
			border-radius: 4px;
			font-size: smaller;
			line-height: 1.5em;
			}
			
			DIV.cms_admin_comments A{
			color: rgb(0, 124, 195) !important;
			}
			
			/*********late add*******/
			
			DIV.page_data{
			margin: 8px 0px;
			height:auto;
			width:auto;
			padding: 12px;
			background: #e9e9e9;
			border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;  
			
			/*rounded corners*/
			-webkit-border-radius: 3px;
			-webkit-border-radius: 3px;
			-moz-border-radius: 3px;
			-moz-border-radius: 3px;
			border-radius: 3px;
			border-radius: 3px;
			}
			
			H1.page_name{
			font-weight: 300;   
			margin: 0px;
			padding: 0px;
			color: #999;
			font-size: 1.6em;
			}
			
			SPAN.site_home_name A{
			font-weight: 600;   
			color: #444;
			}
			
			SPAN.site_parent_page_name A{
			font-weight: 400;
			color: #666;
			}
			
			SPAN.site_page_name{
			font-weight: 300;
			color: #3366FF;
			}
			
			P.page_description{
			margin: 0px;
			padding: 0px;
			/*font-weight: 300;*/
			font-size: .9em;/**/
			margin-top: 12px;
			color: #666;
			}
			
			/******* Horizontal scrolling on list view *******/
			div.list_wrap_n_scroll { 
			overflow-x: auto; 
			}
			.msie6 div.list_wrap_n_scroll,
			.msie7 div.list_wrap_n_scroll,
			.msie8 div.list_wrap_n_scroll { 
			width: 100%;
			padding-bottom: 15px;
			}
			.msie9 div.list_wrap_n_scroll {
			min-height: 0%;
			}
		</style><sys_class_name>content_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>mark.odonnell</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2012-05-03 09:57:39</sys_created_on><sys_id>5040d385efb12000876004167b2256e5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>35</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Gray CSS - Base</sys_name><sys_package display_value="ESS Portal (implemented within Content Management)" source="com.glide.cms.extensions">b58ba2b264e32300aadba650cb85d41a</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>content_css_5040d385efb12000876004167b2256e5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-07-17 06:13:26</sys_updated_on><type>local</type><url/></content_css></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_rectangle_menu_item"><sp_rectangle_menu_item action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><color>default</color><condition>gs.isLoggedIn() && gs.hasRole('itil')&&(!gs.hasRole('admin'));</condition><display_1/><display_2/><display_date/><filter/><glyph>list-alt</glyph><hint/><kb_article/><kb_category/><kb_topic/><label>Orders</label><order>300</order><record_script><![CDATA[// maximum number of entries in this Menu
var max = 100;

var t = data;  // shortcut
t.items = [];

var u = gs.getUser().getID();
//Get user group
var grp1;
var grp = new GlideRecord('sys_user_grmember');
grp.addQuery('user',u);
grp.query();
if(grp.next()){
   grp1 = grp.getValue('group');  
}



//active=true^request.requested_forDYNAMIC='+u

var user = gs.getUser();
t.record_watchers = [];


t.record_watchers.push({'table':'sc_request','filter':'active=true^assignment_group='+grp1});


// use record watchers to tell header when to update dropdown counts


var z1 = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
z1.addEncodedQuery('active=true^assignment_group='+grp1);
z1.addEncodedQuery('active=true^assignment_group='+grp1);
z1.orderByDesc('sys_updated_on');
z1.setLimit(max);
z1.query();
while (z1.next()) {
  if (!z1.canRead())
    continue;
  
  var a1 = {};
  $sp.getRecordValues(a1, z1, 'short_description,sys_id,number,sys_updated_on');
  if (z1.short_description.nil())
    a1.short_description = "(No description)";
  a1.__table = z1.getTableName();
  a1.type = 'record';
  a1.sortOrder = z1.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getNumericValue();
  t.items.push(a1);
}





var z = new GlideRecord('sc_request');
z.addActiveQuery();
if(user.hasRole('admin')){}
else
z.addEncodedQuery('active=true^assignment_group='+grp1);
z.orderByDesc('sys_updated_on');
z.setLimit(max);
z.query();
while (z.next()) {
  if (!z.canRead())
    continue;
  
  var ritm = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
  ritm.addQuery('request', z.getUniqueValue());
  ritm.query();
  if (!ritm.next())
    continue;

  var a = {};
  $sp.getRecordValues(a, z, 'sys_id,number,sys_updated_on');
  if (ritm.hasNext()) // there are multiple items for this request
    a.short_description = ritm.getRowCount() + ' requested items';
  else if (!ritm.canRead()) // only one item, but user cannot see it
  	continue;
  else // one item, and user can see it
    a.short_description = ritm.cat_item.getDisplayValue() || ritm.getDisplayValue("short_description");
  a.__table = z.getTableName();
  a.type = 'request';
  a.sortOrder = z.sys_updated_on.getGlideObject().getNumericValue();
  t.items.push(a);
}

t.items.sort(function(a, b) {
  return b.sortOrder - a.sortOrder;
});
t.items = t.items.slice(0, max); // only want first 30
t.count = t.items.length;

var link = {title: gs.getMessage('View all requests'), type: 'link', href: '?id=requests', items: []};
t.items.unshift(link); // put 'View all requests' first]]></record_script><sc_cat_item/><sc_category/><short_description/><sp_page/><sp_rectangle_menu display_value="NIT Header Menu">4279d942dbeeb30042c8478239961946</sp_rectangle_menu><sp_rectangle_menu_item/><sys_class_name>sp_rectangle_menu_item</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-07-12 08:37:30</sys_created_on><sys_id>bfac9a96db2ef30042c84782399619d0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>16</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Orders</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_rectangle_menu_item_bfac9a96db2ef30042c84782399619d0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-07-17 08:36:16</sys_updated_on><table/><type>scripted</type><url/><url_target/></sp_rectangle_menu_item><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=bfac9a96db2ef30042c84782399619d0"/></record_update>
